CDL Drivers

all employed CDL drivers need to be registered with the Clearinghouse before employment
if they are out of compliance, they can be taken out of service
will need to sign a consent form before any queries can be done
they cannot operate if they have a reported drug and/or alcohol violation without a completed return-to-duty process

